Insider Activity


Individual




William G. Bardel



Mr. William G. Bardel is Independent Director at Black Stone Minerals LP. He is on the Board of Directors at Black Stone Minerals GP LLC and Black Stone Minerals LP.
Mr. Bardel was previously employed as Lead Independent Director by Hudson City Bancorp, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by The Lawrenceville School, a Managing Director by Lehman Brothers, Inc., and a Member by New York City Bar. He also served on the board at Black Stone Natural Resources LLC and Hudson City Savings Bank, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Yale University, a graduate degree from Harvard Law School, and a graduate degree from the University of Oxford.



